item.title: CVE-2023-5041|2024-08-02T07:44:53.783Z -- unknown -- track%20the%20click
item.description: The Track The Click WordPress plugin before 0.3.12 does not properly sanitize query parameters to the stats REST endpoint before using them in a database query, allowing a logged in user with an author role or higher to perform time based blind SQLi attacks on the database.
